Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確認混合氫抽出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:58.36,smallprint,,0010,0000,0000,,H cocktail
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有危險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
